OL,3,C'I never regretted waiving my
OL,4,Canonymity': Gisele Pelicot's statement
OL,5,Cin full
OL,7,FGisele Pelicot thanks supporters in a
OL,8,Fstatement outside court in Avignon,
OL,9,FFrance, after her husband and 50 men
OL,10,Fwere sentenced for sexually assaulting
OL,11,Fher
OL,13,F"This trial was a very difficult test,
OL,14,Fand at this moment, first and
OL,15,Fforemost, I'm thinking of my three
OL,16,Fchildren, David, Caroline and Florian.
