OL,3,C'I never regretted waiving my
OL,4,Canonymity': Gisele Pelicot's statement
OL,5,Cin full
OL,7,FI'm also thinking of my grandchildren
OL,8,Fbecause they are the future - and it
OL,9,Fwas also for them that I led this
OL,10,Ffight. I'm also thinking of Oran and
OL,11,FCelene.
OL,13,FI am also thinking of all the other
OL,14,Ffamilies affected by this. Finally, I
OL,15,Fthink of the victims who have gone
OL,16,Funrecognised, whose stories have often
OL,17,Fstayed in the shadows. I want you to
OL,18,Fknow that we share the same fight.
