OL,3,C'I never regretted waiving my
OL,4,Canonymity': Gisele Pelicot's statement
OL,5,Cin full
OL,7,FI want to express my sincere gratitude
OL,8,Fto all the people who supported me
OL,9,Fevery step of the way on this trial,
OL,10,Fand for their testimony. You gave me
OL,11,Fthe strength to return every day to
OL,12,Fcarry on this difficult trial.
OL,14,FI want to thank the Association of
OL,15,FVictims, your support to me has been
OL,16,Fimmeasurable.
