OL,3,C'I never regretted waiving my
OL,4,Canonymity': Gisele Pelicot's statement
OL,5,Cin full
OL,7,FTo all the journalists who have
OL,8,Ffollowed this since the start, I want
OL,9,Fto express my sincere thanks for your
OL,10,Ftruthful and respectful coverage every
OL,11,Fday for your audience.
OL,13,FFinally, to my lawyers, I want to give
OL,14,Fyou all my thanks for all your support
OL,15,Ffor accompanying me on every step of
OL,16,Fthis very difficult journey.
OL,18,FI wanted, in opening the doors of this
OL,19,Ftrial on the 2nd of September, for
OL,20,Fsociety to see what was happening.
