OL,5,Cin full
OL,7,FI have never regretted this decision.
OL,9,FI now have confidence in our capacity
OL,10,Fto collectively seize a future where
OL,11,Feveryone, men and women, can live in
OL,12,Fharmony in mutual respect and
OL,13,Funderstanding. Thank you."
